snippet.title: CubeHook - A New VR Upcoming Experience
snippet.description:
Steam link: https://store.steampowered.com/app/1815110/CubeHook_VR
Website : http://cubehook.arcarvestudio.com


The new upcoming vr game CubeHook comes to oculus and steam,
Enjoy the lightness and the playful arcade style game.
